r an asset allocation model that matches your risk tolerance and investment time horizon are interested in automatic portfolio rebalancing to maintain your desired asset allocation and ensure that your investment best meets your overall financial objectives our exclusive fee options save you money the select variable annuity offers you two purchase options for maximum flexibility and cost savings with the frontload design you pay the sales charge up front but your annual expense charges will be lower and you’ll have access to your funds with no withdrawal charges the backload design lets you put  percent of your money to work for you right away but it is subject to withdrawal charges and higher costs initially northwestern mutual is one of the few companies that provide a unique conversion feature when you purchase the backload plan we’ll convert you to frontload pricing once we have covered our expenses — sometimes in as little as a few years depending on the value of your annuity this conversion feature helps you reduce your mortality and expense costs and may enhance the longterm value of your annuity more on this topic click on the links below to access more information variable annuities variable annuities learn how a variable annuity can offer distinct advantages that may give you more flexibility in retirement watch building income for your retirement with the select™ variable annuity building income for your retirement with the select™ variable annuity learn about the northwestern mutual select™ variable annuity download how to fund your ira and other taxqualified plans how to fund your ira and other taxqualified plans learn about iras and other taxqualified plans download mutual funds and variable annuities mutual funds and variable annuities learn about your funding options download related links variable products compensation prospectuses and reports deferred annuity daily unit values fund information income plan daily unit values performance history want